responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "68BA319D49F806EA006EA3886D9502A8", "Oh very well! The curious costumers have off and lost themselves in the undervaults of Bloom. Behind the red veil if you have the key. They sound quite tasty. I\'d gladly feast on their bones with you, deary. Ha, ha, ha!")
